        <h1>Help Center</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the Help Center! Here you can find answers to your questions and get assistance with our services.</p>

        <h2>Common Questions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#faq1">How do I book a ride?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#faq2">What payment methods do you accept?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#faq3">How can I change my booking?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#faq4">What should I do if I have an issue during my ride?</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="faq1">How do I book a ride?</h2>
        <p>To book a ride, simply visit the Ride page, enter your details, and confirm your booking.</p>

        <h2 id="faq2">What payment methods do you accept?</h2>
        <p>We accept various payment methods including credit/debit cards and online payment platforms.</p>

        <h2 id="faq3">How can I change my booking?</h2>
        <p>You can change your booking by visiting your account page and selecting the booking you wish to modify.</p>

        <h2 id="faq4">What should I do if I have an issue during my ride?</h2>
        <p>If you encounter any issues during your ride, please contact our customer support immediately for assistance.</p>
    </div>

